                "The keyword ~x0 is not a legal keyword for a :BDD hint.  The ~
                 hint ~x1 is therefore illegal.  See :DOC hints."
                (car rest) top-arg)))))
         (er-let*@par
          ((cdr-alist
            (translate-bdd-hint1@par top-arg (cddr rest) ctx wrld state)))
